# Use Case Testing

Use Case Testing focuses on validating end-to-end user scenarios based on real user behavior.

## Example
Online store â€“ purchase flow

## Use Case: Buy a product

### Actor : Registered user

### Preconditions
- User is logged in
- Product is available in stock

### Main Flow
1. User opens product page
2. User adds product to cart
3. User opens cart
4. User proceeds to checkout
5. User enters delivery details
6. User confirms order

### Expected Result
- Order is successfully placed
- Confirmation message is displayed

## Alternative Flows
- Product is out of stock
- Payment is declined
- User cancels checkout

## Conclusion
Use case testing ensures critical user flows work as expected.

